WEBVTT

00:02:59.760 --> 00:03:03.363
Measles outbreaks have been reported
in multiple US states.

00:03:03.387 --> 00:03:04.783
And many have forgotten,

00:03:04.807 --> 00:03:08.188
but measles is very
infectious and dangerous.

00:03:08.498 --> 00:03:12.299
Just a few viral particles
can infect an individual.

00:03:12.743 --> 00:03:14.815
And there have been even reports

00:03:14.839 --> 00:03:17.259
at sporting events
and at an Olympic stadium

00:03:17.283 --> 00:03:19.973
where the virus, through the air,
travels long distances

00:03:19.997 --> 00:03:22.980
and infects a vulnerable
person in the crowd.

00:03:23.288 --> 00:03:25.399
In fact, if I had
a measles cough right now,

00:03:25.423 --> 00:03:26.580
(Coughs)

00:03:26.604 --> 00:03:30.747
somebody in the back
of this auditorium could get infected.